---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
import Line from "./Line.astro"
---

<section>
  <h2>Consider hosting an event at Rosenhøj for an unforgettable experience.</h2>
  <img src="../images/Events2.png" alt="Events" />
  <p>
    With vintage-inspired surroundings and the ability to cater to up to 40 guests, we offer an ideal setting for any occasion - whether it's a confirmation, birthday party, or company event. <br />
    <br />
    Our expert chef will craft delicious menus to meet your specific preferences and dietary requirements. Whether you desire a formal dinner or a casual buffet, we can cater to your needs with high-quality
    cuisine and exceptional service.
  </p>

  <img src="../images/Events1.png" alt="Events" />

  <p>
    Our dedicated team will assist you in every aspect of planning, including table settings, decor, music, and entertainment, to ensure your event is a resounding success. We pride ourselves on
    delivering outstanding service and attention to detail, so you can relax and enjoy your special occasion.
  </p>
  <p>Get in touch with us today to learn more about our event packages and menu options. We'd be honored to host your next special event at Rosenhøj.</p>
</section>
<Button text="Contact Us" link="" />
<Line/>
<style>
  section {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: auto;
  }
  h2 {
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--dark_blue);
  }
  h2::after {
    display: none;
  }
  img {
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: bottom;
  }
  @media (min-width: 800px) {
    section {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1300px;
    }
    p{
      max-width: 55ch;
    }

    h2 {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
    img:first-of-type,
    p:nth-of-type(2),
    p:nth-of-type(3) {
      grid-column: 2/3;
    }
    img:last-of-type,
    p:first-of-type {
      grid-column: 1/2;
    }
    img:first-of-type,
    p:first-of-type {
      grid-row: 2/3;
    }
    img:last-of-type {
      grid-row: span 2;
    }
  }
</style>
